OL,3,CHow to host the Irish Open
OL,5,FThe Irish Open returns to Royal County
OL,6,FDown for the first time in nine years
OL,7,Fthis Thursday.
OL,9,FWhen the curtain comes down on Sunday
OL,10,Fafternoon, the winning golfer will
OL,11,Fhave played 72 holes of gruelling golf
OL,12,Fover four days in front of 16,000 fans
OL,13,Feach day.
OL,15,FHowever, for all of that to happen and
OL,16,Fto run smoothly, it requires a mammoth
OL,17,Feffort involving hundreds of staff and
OL,18,Fvolunteers.
