OL,3,CHow to host the Irish Open
OL,5,FCourse Manager Eammon Crawford knows
OL,6,Fall about getting one of golf's
OL,7,Fshining lights up to tournament speed,
OL,8,Fwith the work beginning in the dark:
OL,9,F"We will be starting at 4am each day
OL,10,Fand at that time it is pretty dark.
OL,12,F"So every machine will have a light
OL,13,Fon, every person will have a headlamp
OL,14,Fon, even the boys doing divots in the
OL,15,Ffairway.
