OL,3,CHow to host the Irish Open
OL,5,FEammon also gives an insight into the
OL,6,Famount of people required to keep the
OL,7,Fcourse in great shape: "To get it
OL,8,Fready at the minute I have 18 full-
OL,9,Ftime staff and six temporary staff,
OL,10,Fcaddies and that helping us out, doing
OL,11,Fbunkers and divots and that there.
OL,13,F"Coming near the weekend we will be
OL,14,Fbringing in 20 staff from golf clubs
OL,15,Fall across Ireland."
OL,17,FLike all links courses, Royal County
OL,18,FDown is protected by a large amount of
OL,19,Fbunkers, and they require a lot of
OL,20,Feffort to keep them up to scratch.
