OL,3,CHow to host the Irish Open
OL,5,FHead professional Kevan Whitson hopes
OL,6,Fthey will enhance the experience for
OL,7,Fthe players: "We have added a couple
OL,8,Fof new bunkers that are superb
OL,9,Factually, we have got a great visual
OL,10,Fbunker up on the left hand side of the
OL,11,F8th hole and up the left hand side of
OL,12,Fthe 5th hole.
OL,14,F"We have done a little bit of work
OL,15,Fover on the 17th, on the approach to
OL,16,Fthe green there."
